<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink231-kilavi">oruvaḻittaṇantuvanta talaimakaṟkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante told the hero who went away briefly. 
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink231">
<l>yāṅkuval lunaiyō vōṅkal veṟpa</l>
<l>virumpal kūntaṟ ṟiruntiḻai yarivai</l>
<l>titalai māmai tēyap</l>
<l>pacalai pāyap pirivu teyyō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>How are you able,</l> 	
        <l rend="indent2">o man from the lofty mountain,</l>  
   
        <l rend="space indent">for the beauty-spotted darkness</l> 	
        <l rend="indent">of the young woman</l> 
        <l rend="indent">with dark, many tresses and perfect ornaments, to fade,</l>  
        <l rend="indent">and for [her] pallor to spread,</l>   
   
        <l rend="space">[to handle the] separation, alas?</l>  
   
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
